data.name: The Agent of Mystery - Earth
data.desc: When this card is Normal Summoned, you can add 1 "The Agent" monster from your Deck to your hand, except "The Agent of Mystery - Earth". While "The Sanctuary in the Sky" is face-up on the field, you can add 1 "Master Hyperion" from your Deck to your hand instead.

card_sets.set_name: Ghosts From the Past: The 2nd Haunting
